article_id:1719,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Facility Event, The Phantom's Ransom, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f532c932c025c42516ae104bf09f3dc5.png,message:<div>A new facility event, The Phantom&#39;s Ransom, will begin at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>!<br><br>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the light element. You&#39;ll also be able to get an event-related reward facility!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f532c932c025c42516ae104bf09f3dc5.png"></div><div>The Speranza Opera Troupe receives a letter from Lapis, the phantom thief, in which she threatens to abduct their lead singer, Belladonna. Despite the Prince and friends&#39; best efforts to protect her, Lapis manages to spirit the star performer away. In order to save Belladonna, the show must go on&mdash;but who will take the stage as the next prima donna? It&#39;s time for none other than the pirate captain Karina to shine!<br><br>â– Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604901599"></span><br><br>Notes:<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1603432800,update_time1603355889